   - Pattern at stream end (worst case, full scan)
   - Pattern distributed uniformly (average case)
   - Pattern absent (negative case)
3. **Metrics**: Throughput (GB/s), latency per match, cache miss rate
4. **Variables**: Pattern length (16/32 bytes), server topology effects

